    "An appropriate range is specified for calculating the [minNumRule -maxNumRule] rules and a scoring threshold parameter for identifying rat- ings (likes and dislikes).",
    "Based on this rating which falls under the set of these rules, collaborative and target customers are identified to provide personalized recommendations to match customers' choices with items.",
